<br>
It is with regret that I must inform you, the populace, of a dramatic change in the political structure of our fair city.  Our esteemed Prinzessin, Marie Mercer-Renald and her Seneschal, Grifon Blackmore, have been called to duty by those in power in the Camarilla.  This call has forced them to effectively abandon their posts here in Santa Carla.  This is a heavy blow to this city.  The Camarilla Kollegium seems to have plans for our now former Prinzessin and Seneschal which we are not privy to.  Frau Mercer-Renald, Herr Blackmore and I have met on this situation, and Her Highness has invested myself as Vertrauensmann der Arbeiter or Steward of Santa Carla until such time as a suitable candidate for Prince presents themselves.<br>
In the interim, I, along with the Primogen Kollegium will act in the missing Prince’s stead.  As Steward, I will act as Seneschal and a voice on the Primogen Kollegium.  As such, I will abdicate my position as Nosferatu Primogen and nominate my clansman Zarthas as Primogen in my stead.<br>
In light of recent events, I must ask members of the following clans to nominate someone in your clan to represent you in the Primogen Kollegium; Gangrel, Ventrue and Clan Toreador, unless Frauline Estelle returns by this Friday evening.  <br>
If there is one among you who wishes to claim Praxis and take the throne, you must have the approval of the Primogen.  We will not allow just any Cainite to assume control of this city without say.  If you presume to take the throne by force, I would recommend you reconsider your plan of action.  I will personally take exception to a violent uprising and take appropriate actions with the aid of those of the other Primogen if need be.<br>
If you have questions, please do not hesitate to voice them to me.  I will return all inquiries with as much haste as I can.<br>
<br>
Dienst haben,<br>
<br>
Graf Orlock<br>
Vertrauensmann der Arbeiter ein Santa Carla<br>
